      <h3>3. User Responsibilities</h3>
      <p>You agree to provide accurate information and use our services for lawful purposes only.</p>
      <h3>4. Limitation of Liability</h3>
      <p>ANVI REALTORS shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use of our services.</p>
      <h3>5. Governing Law</h3>
      <p>These terms are governed by the laws of India, and any disputes shall be subject to the jurisdiction of Mumbai courts.</p>
      <p>For full terms, contact us at anvirealtorsdata@gmail.com</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>

<!-- FOOTER -->
